{"tid":419591,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"煲中藥問題","createTime":"2017-09-30T15:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T15:28:11.000Z","uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b43aef90f3128ca1c4cf9bd3f254c67d788758f","tid":419591,"uid":27510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:24:41.000Z","msg":"有冇人煲中藥都係用電子藥煲？<br />\n想問係咪會用得多d時間？<br />\n<br />\n因為個中醫本身叫我用普通不銹鋼煲，大火煲30分鐘+30分鐘就得<br />\n咁我唔係好識就叫屋企人幫我整<br />\n但我屋企人用電子藥煲，煲左1個鐘+1個鐘都未煲完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我驚出到黎個效果會冇咁好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇中醫/都係用電子煲既巴絲可以答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097ef34893c91f183022d121f520fe76ebc15c6d","tid":419591,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}